<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Emodius</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-29 14:33:15</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>In response to the last comment block posted:<BR>
<BR>
Snare is a spell not unlike most others in that initailly oyu will have trouble with its application and duration. Increasing your appropriate magic skill and gaining levels will help. Every (and i mean EVERY) druid i play with uses this spell every combat they are in, unless they require NO movement from the target. Stick with this spell (and yes i understand its a bad thing to have a mon agro on you at full speed so practice on lower level mobs) and it will serve you well. <BR>
<BR>
Good luck<BR>
<BR>
Elmo<BR>
Level 45 Wiz</font></td></tr></table>
